    <h1 class="page-title">Peoples of Ormandia</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle"><em>From the Realm Codex, the free compendium of all knowledge pertaining to the Known World</em></p>

    <div class="toc">
      <div class="toc-title">Contents</div>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#historical">Historical Peoples</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contemporary">Contemporary Peoples</a></li>
